headline: 4 Industrial Manufacturing Stocks to Gain Despite Industry Headwinds
summary: Slowdown in new orders, supply-chain issues and rising costs weigh on the Zacks Manufacturing - General Industrial industry's near-term prospects. DOV, RBC, AIT and DNOW are a few stocks to gain.
